              <path d="M 0 50 L 106.67 0 L 213.33 50 L 320 0 L 426.67 50 L 533.33 0 L 640 50 L 746.67 0 L 853.33 50 L 960 0 L 1066.67 50 L 1173.33 0 L 1280 50 L 1280 100 L 0 100 Z" fill="currentColor"></path>
